<div class="big-container">
  <article class="article">
    <div style="width:fit-content;padding:10px;height:auto;background-color:rgb(0,102,255);border-radius:10px;">
      <h3 style="text-align:center;color:#fff;">清单</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="topsign-title">
      <h2 class="topsign-text">这里是AKlassen的书单/歌单/待办(～￣▽￣)～</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);">推荐的书/游戏/歌</p>
    </div>

    <script>
      function selectTab(id){
        ['book','play','game'].forEach(function(t){
          document.getElementById(t).style.display = (t===id) ? 'block' : 'none';
          var btn = document.getElementById('tab-'+t);
          if (t===id) {
            btn.style.background = 'var(--text-link)';
            btn.style.color = '#fff';
          } else {
            btn.style.background = 'var(--bg-secondary)';
            btn.style.color = 'var(--text-primary)';
          }
        });
      }
    </script>

    <div class="sign-container" style="padding:15px;margin-bottom:15px;">
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:15px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <button id="tab-book" onclick="selectTab('book')" style="cursor:pointer;padding:6px 20px;border:none;border-radius:20px;background:var(--text-link);color:#fff;font-size:14px;transition:all 0.3s ease;">书单</button>
        <button id="tab-play" onclick="selectTab('play')" style="cursor:pointer;padding:6px 20px;border:none;border-radius:20px;background:var(--bg-secondary);color:var(--text-primary);font-size:14px;transition:all 0.3s ease;">歌单</button>
        <button id="tab-game" onclick="selectTab('game')" style="cursor:pointer;padding:6px 20px;border:none;border-radius:20px;background:var(--bg-secondary);color:var(--text-primary);font-size:14px;transition:all 0.3s ease;">游戏</button>
      </div>

      <div id="book">
        <div style="border-style:dashed;width:80%;height:auto;padding:5px;border-width:3px;border-color:rgb(0,102,255);border-radius:10px;margin:10px auto;">
          <p style="text-align:center;font-size:15px;font-family:Impact,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,102,255);">不那么硬核的</p>
        </div>
        <div class="book-holder">
          <div class="book-cover" style="background-image:url(https://img.soyorin.work/books/introduction_to_algorithm.jpg);"></div>
          <div class="book-intro"><p>《算法导论》（Introduction to Algorithms）是麻省理工学院出版社出版的关于计算机中数据结构与算法的图书，作者是托马斯·科尔曼（Thomas H. Cormen）、查尔斯·雷瑟尔森（Charles E. Leiserson）、罗纳德·李维斯特（Ronald L. Rivest）、克利福德·斯坦（Clifford Stein）。第一版刊行于1990年，2009年最新版为第三版。<br>本书深入浅出，全面地介绍了计算机算法。对每一个算法的分析既易于理解又十分有趣，并保持了数学严谨性。本书的设计目标全面，适用于多种用途。</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="book-holder">
          <div class="book-cover" style="background-image:url(https://img.soyorin.work/books/politics_and_history.jpg);"></div>
          <div class="book-intro"><p>Enlightenment advances towards a science of politics, and Marx's relationship to Hegel.<br><br>In the first two essays of this book, Louis Althusser analyses the work of two of the greatest thinkers of the Enlightenment - Montesquieu and Rousseau.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="book-holder">
          <div class="book-cover" style="background-image:url(https://img.soyorin.work/books/pour_marx.jpg);"></div>
          <div class="book-intro"><p>Pour Marx is a 1965 book by the philosopher Louis Althusser, a leading theoretician of the PCF, in which the author reinterprets the work of the philosopher Karl Marx, proposing an epistemological break between the young, Hegelian Marx, and the old Marx, the author of Das Kapital.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="book-holder">
          <div class="book-cover" style="background-image:url(https://img.soyorin.work/books/princeton_calculus.jpg);"></div>
          <div class="book-intro"><p>The Calculus Lifesaver combines ease of use and readability with the depth of content and mathematical rigor of the best calculus textbooks. It is an indispensable volume for any student seeking to master calculus.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="book-holder">
          <div class="book-cover" style="background-image:url(https://img.soyorin.work/books/the_sublime_subject_of_ideology.jpg);"></div>
          <div class="book-intro"><p>Žižek thematizes the Kantian notion of the sublime in order to liken ideology to the experience of something that is absolutely vast and powerful beyond all perception and objective intelligibility.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div style="border-style:dashed;width:80%;height:auto;padding:5px;border-width:3px;border-color:rgb(0,102,255);border-radius:10px;margin:10px auto;">
          <p style="text-align:center;font-size:15px;font-family:Impact,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,102,255);">硬核的</p>
        </div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Software Foundations</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Database systems: A Practical Approach to Design, Implementation, and Management</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Computational Complexity: A Modern Approach - Sanjeev Arora & Boaz Barak</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Types and Programming Languages - Benjamin C. Pierce</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Discrete Mathmatics and Its Application - Kenneth H·Rosen</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Computer System: A Programmer's Perspective (CS:APP) - Randal E.Bryant</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Structure and Interpretation of Computer Language (SICP)</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>TCP/IP Illustrated - W·Richard Stevens</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Modern Compiler Implementation in C - Andrew W.Appel</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Modern Compiler Implementation in Java - Andrew W.Appel</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Assembly Language for x86 Processors - Kip Irvine</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Advanced Compiler Design and Implementation - Steven.S.Muchnick</p></div></div>
        <div class="book-holder-full"><div class="book-intro-full"><p>Engineering a Compiler - Keith Cooper</p></div></div>
        <div style="border-style:dashed;width:80%;height:auto;padding:5px;border-width:3px;border-color:rgb(0,102,255);border-radius:10px;margin:10px auto;">
          <p style="text-align:center;font-size:15px;font-family:Impact,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,102,255);">愿望单</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="play" style="display:none;">
        <p style="text-align:center;color:var(--text-muted);padding:40px 0;">歌单建设中...</p>
      </div>

      <div id="game" style="display:none;">
        <p style="text-align:center;color:var(--text-muted);padding:40px 0;">游戏列表建设中...</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</div>
